item.content:encoded:
An unique wooden puzzle, mysterious lion is the perfect choice as a gift

Each piece is animal shaped, making this a unique puzzle and a fabulous gift and is more challenging compared with other jigsaw puzzles.

Jigsaw puzzles can promote eye-hand coordination, improve concentration, patience, logical thinking and problem-solving skills. 

Suitable For Adults and Children aged 8+

Product Features:

– wooden pieces made from formaldehyde-free sea birch

–  decorated with high quality paint

– arrives in  a premium wooden gift box

Product Specification:

Material: wood

Finished product size: 28X20.4CM

Carton size: 21X15X4CM (Due to manual measurement, there will be an error of 1-3mm.)

Number of pieces: 186 pieces
